latestPosts.caption:
If you’re wondering what I was upto in that video…

In Milan, there’s a tradition that says if you want your wish to come true, you have to stand on the mosaic of the bull at Galleria Vittorio Emanuele II, place your right heel on its *beep🤐* and spin around three times.

My wish did come true, has yours?

One can’t blame the Neapolitans for saying, ‘Vedi Napoli e poi muori!’

[ Napoleon Napoli Naples Pizza Italy Europe]
From the mountains to the sea, captivated by the stunning landscapes of Wadi Shab 🌊
Seriously, wine is cheaper than water here🍷

Note to self: 

Do you ever find yourself sitting, reflecting on the past year, and suddenly feeling embarrassed by all the clumsy moments that come rushing back? You know, those times when you think, “Wow, my younger self was so immature”?

I think I’ve finally reached that point in life where, looking back at this year, I can honestly say to my younger self, “I’m proud of the risks you took and the decisions you made.”

It’s a little moment of self-recognition for all the milestones I’ve achieved. 

All in all, it was a very happy birthday indeed🎈

Make a wish 🧚🏻‍♀️ ✨
